---
title: HelloHero: Spiced Beef Rump & Currant Couscous with Yoghurt & Almonds
description: Couscous — the grain so nice they named it twice! Here we’ve added sweet currants and nutty almonds for a pop of flavour and topped the whole thing off with mildly spiced beef rump and greens. Don’t forget the generous dollop of cooling yoghurt to bring the meal together.
